    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5064884>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–11. Ankistromeces dunwichensis n. sp. from intertrabecular spaces of ventricle and atrium (heart) of Siganus fuscescens off North Stradbroke Island. 9. Adult. Dorsal anteriorly, medially twisting laterally at level of “arrow a”, ventral side to the right, whole mount. 10. Male terminal genitalia, lateral view. 11. Female terminal genitalia, lateral view. Vitelline duct omitted as obscures path of proximal uterus. Oviduct not observed in single specimen. Scale­bars: 9,11, 250" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5064884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

